rows.label: qst105305_msg002
rows.name: Thank you for the subjugation.

rows.label: qst105305_msg003
rows.name:
I'm sorry to ask again, but I need
you to help with resupplying.

rows.label: qst105305_msg004
rows.name:
We brought enough food, but our
medicine is being consumed rapidly.

rows.label: qst105305_msg005
rows.name: What was that just now...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0001
rows.name: You've come! What a relief.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0002
rows.name:
Because the BQ1053 Snow-Mountain
Carnivores were reduced
earlier than usual...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0003
rows.name:
...the BQ1053 small Titan Parasites
that were their prey have
multiplied in great numbers.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0004
rows.name:
Because of that, we were
unexpectedly attacked during
our move, and many were injured...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0005
rows.name:
It's only a matter of time before
we run out of medicine...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0006
rows.name:
We're relying on you completely...
It's truly pathetic...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0007
rows.name:
If you gather the materials
for medicine and give them
to me, we'll be fine.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0008
rows.name: We are counting on you.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0101
rows.name: Did you bring the materials?

rows.label: qst105305_msg0121
rows.name:
It seems we still don't
have enough to make the
required amount of medicine.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0122
rows.name:
We would appreciate your
cooperation in gathering them.

rows.label: qst105305_msg0151
rows.name:
We have gathered enough materials
to make the necessary medicine!

rows.label: qst105305_msg0152
rows.name: Thank you very mu...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0153
rows.name:
That sound just now... It
didn't sound like a BQ11053
small Titan Parasite...

rows.label: qst105305_msg0154
rows.name: Could you please go and check?
